## 🚀 Quick Start

### Create Full Stack Rust Project

```bash
# Option 1: Leptos Full Stack
cargo install leptos-cli
cargo leptos new my-app --git https://github.com/leptos-rs/start

# Option 2: Dioxus Full Stack
cargo install dioxus-cli
dx new my-app
cd my-app
dx serve --fullstack

# Option 3: Manual Workspace
cargo new --lib my-fullstack-app
cd my-fullstack-app
mkdir -p crates/{shared,backend,frontend}
```

